@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Reviewed : approve
OnHold : entry / log catalog
Reviewed --> Processing : update
Processing --> Completed : confirm
Completed --> Created : cancel
Completed : entry / log catalog
Created --> Approved : submit
Approved --> [*]
@enduml